  "title": "Securing Serverless Handlers using FastAPI with Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide provides a step-by-step approach to securing your serverless functions built with FastAPI and Python 3.12+. It covers important aspects such as authentication, authorization, and handling sensitive data.",

